            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 922,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01My4rBsFF6QhWFMSFFjFkk3\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Welcome, Brave Adventurer! 🎭\\n\\nGreetings, traveler! I am the Keeper of Tales, and you stand at the threshold of an epic adventure. But first, every hero needs a proper introduction!\\n\\n**Tell me, what shall I call you?** \\n\\nYou may give me:\\n- Your real name\\n- A heroic alias\\n- Or let me surprise you with a ridiculous nickname!\\n\\n*The wind whispers through ancient trees, and somewhere in the distance, a dragon yawns. Your story is about to begin...*\\n\\nWhat name shall echo through the ages? 🗡️✨\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":15,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":143,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
