            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01HTetavafzy4sSbg3gxecYq\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"# Behold! Your Destiny Has a Name! 🎪\\n\\n*The mystical winds swirl, ancient runes glow, and the universe consults its sense of humor...*\\n\\n**From this day forth, you shall be known as:**\\n\\n## 🌟 **Sir Snacksworth the Peckish** 🌟\\n\\n*Legendary hero whose stomach rumbles louder than thunder, whose quest for glory is only interrupted by quests for sandwiches, and whose battle cry is \\\"But first, elevenses!\\\"*\\n\\n---\\n\\nNow then, **Sir Snacksworth the Peckish**, your adventure awaits! \\n\\n**Choose your path:**\\n\\n1. 🏰 **The Haunted Castle of Nope** - Spooky, mysterious, probably has ghosts (definitely has ghosts)\\n2. 🌲 **The Enchanted Forest of Questionable Decisions** - Magical creatures, talking trees, and at least three curses\\n3. 🏔️ **The Mountain of Regret** - Very tall, very cold, named by the last guy who climbed it\\n4. 🏴‍☠️ **The Pirate Cove of Mild Inconvenience** - Pirates who are more annoying than dangerous\\n\\nWhere does your hunger for adventure (and possibly actual hunger) lead you first? ⚔️\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":164,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":318,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
