            "size": 937,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_01AyD7s4r29NgfrppztVVtXR\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Ah, a fresh patient! Welcome, welcome, **Chuckles Von Snortington**!\\n\\n*scribbles something on clipboard with a thermometer*\\n\\nExcellent, excellent. Now, before we begin, I need to ask you the standard medical questions: Have you ever been to New Jersey? Do you believe in vitamins? And most importantly - can you see why kids love the taste of Cinnamon Toast Crunch?\\n\\nWhat brings you to my office today? And please, don't say \\\"the door\\\" - I've heard that one three times this week and I'm still not sure if it's a symptom.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":142,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":140,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
