        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1102,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1102,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_0132BMSxCuhRpEu9e8kuPX1z\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"*adjusts stethoscope backwards*\\n\\nAh, hello there, **Captain Crunch-N-Munch**! \\n\\nWelcome, welcome! Please, have a seat on the examining table—or is that the supply closet? I can never tell in this light. Now, what seems to be the problem today? And before you answer, I should mention that I don't technically believe in \\\"germs.\\\" They're more of a theory, really. Like gravity, or the moon.\\n\\n*flips through a magazine instead of a medical chart*\\n\\nSo, what brings you to see me? Mysterious ailment? Routine check-up? Or did you just want to discuss my latest medical breakthrough—I've discovered that the human body can survive on a diet of exclusively gummy vitamins and confidence!\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":18,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":176,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
