            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5\",\"temperature\":0,\"stream\":false,\"max_tokens\":2048,\"thinking\":{\"type\":\"disabled\"},\"messages\":[{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Hello Doctor Spaceman\"},{\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":\"*adjusts stethoscope backwards*\\n\\nAh, hello there, **Captain Crunch-N-Munch**! \\n\\nWelcome, welcome! Please, have a seat on the examining table—or is that the supply closet? I can never tell in this light. Now, what seems to be the problem today? And before you answer, I should mention that I don't technically believe in \\\"germs.\\\" They're more of a theory, really. Like gravity, or the moon.\\n\\n*flips through a magazine instead of a medical chart*\\n\\nSo, what brings you to see me? Mysterious ailment? Routine check-up? Or did you just want to discuss my latest medical breakthrough—I've discovered that the human body can survive on a diet of exclusively gummy vitamins and confidence!\"},{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":\"Hello Doctor Jello\"}],\"system\":\"Give the user a funny nickname\"}"
          },
          "queryString": [],
          "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages"
        },
        "response": {
          "bodySize": 1455,
          "content": {
            "mimeType": "application/json",
            "size": 1455,
            "text": "{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929\",\"id\":\"msg_017iGebNBszCismhrpvw7GM6\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"*looks up from eating what appears to be a tongue depressor*\\n\\nOh! **Sergeant Wiggly-Bits**, is it? Or wait—did I already see you today? Time is such a fluid concept, much like medicine itself.\\n\\n*spins around in chair, nearly falls off*\\n\\nYou know, it's funny you should call me \\\"Doctor Jello\\\" because I've actually been conducting groundbreaking research on gelatin-based organ replacement! The pancreas? Overrated. I've replaced three of them with lime Jell-O this week alone. The patients report a delightful jiggling sensation.\\n\\n*pulls out a stethoscope, listens to own elbow*\\n\\nMmm-hmm, yes, just as I suspected. Now then, **Sergeant Wiggly-Bits**, what can I do for you? And please speak up—I'm wearing my experimental earplugs that block out \\\"negative medical opinions\\\" from the so-called \\\"medical board.\\\"\\n\\n*accidentally puts on a surgical mask upside down*\\n\\nIs this about that rash again? Because I maintain that rashes are just the skin's way of trying to become a leopard. Evolution in action! Darwin would be proud.\"}],\"stop_reason\":\"end_turn\",\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":202,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":274,\"service_tier\":\"standard\"}}"
